                "invention-title": [
                    "Quaternary ammonium low-viscosity ionic eutectic absorbent capable of efficiently and reversibly absorbing CO2",
                    "一种高效可逆吸收CO2的季铵类低粘离子型低共熔吸收剂"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a quaternary ammonium low-viscosity ionic eutectic absorbent capable of efficiently and reversibly absorbing CO2, and belongs to the technical field of gas separation and purification. The functional ionic liquid is generated by quaternary ammonium strong base and nitrogen heterocyclic ring through acid-base neutralization reaction. The novel low-viscosity eutectic absorbent is compounded by quaternary ammonium functional ionic liquid and polyhydric alcohols according to a certain proportion. The eutectic absorbent realizes efficient separation of CO2 through chemical absorption, physical absorption and hydrogen-bond interaction. The ionic eutectic absorbent has the advantages of simple synthesis, high CO2 absorption amount, high absorption-desorption cycle stability, low viscosity before and after absorption and the like, and a novel absorbent is provided for separation and purification of CO2 in flue gas, natural gas and industrial carbon-containing tail gas."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种高效可逆吸收CO2的季铵类低粘离子型低共熔吸收剂，属于气体分离与净化技术领域。所述功能离子液体由季铵类的强碱与氮杂环通过酸碱中和反应生成。新型低粘低共熔吸收剂通过季铵类功能离子液体与多元醇按照一定比例复配。低共熔吸收剂通过化学吸收、物理吸收及氢键作用实现对CO2的高效分离。所述离子型低共熔吸收剂具有合成简单，CO2吸收量高，吸收‑解吸循环稳定性高，吸收前后粘度低等优点，为烟气、天然气、工业含碳尾气中CO2的分离净化提供一种新型吸收剂。"
                }
            ]
